            <!-- Question 2 -->
            <div class="mb-8 p-6 bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-4 mb-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">Question 2 (4 marks)</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2 font-medium">
                  Explain how GitHub enhances collaborative software development beyond basic version control functionality.
                </p>
