                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="mb-4">
                <div class="border-l-4 border-gray-300 pl-4">
                  <div class="space-y-3">
                    <div>
                      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 mb-1">Local Repository:</p>
                      <div class="space-y-2">
